            <h5><a href="/card/LL04-065/">LL04-065 "Humming Friend"</a></h5>
            <div class="seealso">
                See also: <a href="/faq/general#join_success_order">What is the order for <%- skillFormat("[Live Join]/[Live Success]") %>
                    Skills?</a>
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="065">
                The Members joining this <%- skillFormat("⟪LIVE⟫ have 3x [SMILE] and 1x [ALL]") %> in total. Will the requirement be reduced to 2?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                No. This Skill requires four or more Pieces of one of the Attribute types <%- skillFormat("[SMILE], [PURE], [COOL] or [ALL]. You cannot count [ALL]") %> as a Piece of an Attribute of your choice.
